                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="352r">1v-352r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA">قران</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>بسم الله الرحمنم الرحيم الحمد لله رب العالمني الرحمن الرحيم ملك يوم الدين</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#352r">-352r</locus>الذي يوسوس في صدور الناس من الجنة والناس</explicit>
                     <note>Substantial lacuna between fols 349 and 350: fol. 349v contains the beginning of sūra 79 and fol. 350r contains the end of sūra 98. Sūra 114 on fols 351v-352r is added in a different hand. Fol. 352 is modern note paper with blue rulings. Fols 236-331 and 347-352 smudged. Words divided into two lines. </note>
                     <note/>
